’Щ@d7d05bfb6d8764d656fe96215b6434e149bcd08e54c185449e9e1671eec05361Щ…Title: title: url encode
Path: Flags
Content:
``--all, -a``
: Encode all non-alphanumeric chars including 
``/``
, 
``.``
, 
``:``
.
